00:28:35.005 --> 00:28:36.215
<i>Nobody</i>

543
00:28:36.381 --> 00:28:38.091
<i>Right here. right now
ls all we got</i>

544
00:28:40.385 --> 00:28:41.261
<i>A little party</i>

545
00:28:41.428 --> 00:28:42.846
<i>Never killed nobody</i>

546
