...Rome. Vienna...

680
00:36:54.045 --> 00:36:55.171
...Zurich. Helsinki...

681
00:36:55.380 --> 00:36:56.756
...Moscow. Istanbul...

682
00:36:56.965 --> 00:36:58.049
...collecting jewels...

683
